“For Americans, London is an easy pick for a getaway because the city has no language barrier and offers great cultural attractions, from theater to museums,” said Misty Belles, Virtuoso’s global head of public relations. “And, since the value of the pound has dropped since Brexit, visiting is less expensive than it has been for many years.”
